This is a guessing game. The computer will randomly pick froma set of numbers 1-100 and the user will try and choose the number the computer selected. 
*/

Computer shows numbers 1-100 on screen
Computer shows scoreboard of 10 points
Computer randomly selects a number in between 1 & 100, call this number n

Promt user to "click a number", call this number s
If s>n prompt "lower" and scratch all numbers >s
If s<n prompt "higher" and scratch all numbers <s
Decrease scoreboard by 1 for every s>n and s<n
Repeat prompts until s=n
If s=n then prompt "Congrats!" 
